description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Calisthenics For Beginners (DAILY ROUTINE)' from the channel itsdrewmoemeka.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Here's a workout routine for people new to calisthenics. Try it out for a couple weeks and I'll be back with a new workout video to challenge you with!
